1. Using x11 on mac to enable the linux gui 
    ref: https://uisapp2.iu.edu/confluence-prd/pages/viewpage.action?pageId=280461906
    on mac you should add -X option after ssh comand (The typo on the ref page)

2. Terminal theme on mac can be set by "./configs/macTerminalTheme/Xcode_style.terminal". And use the terminal preference to set it as default.
